Installation: 

1) Copy the contents of the mt-static and plugins directories to the appropriate directories in Movable Type or Melody.
2) Run chmod 755 on plugins/mtTouch and plugins/mtTouch/mt-mttouch.cgi or the Ajax functionality for loading more entries will not work.
